00:04:22.570 --> 00:04:24.600
It is more of a state of mind.

00:04:24.600 --> 00:04:25.660
Be comfortable.

00:04:25.660 --> 00:04:29.500
Be comfortable around others and people are
going to forget about the clothing, but also

00:04:29.500 --> 00:04:34.660
